with the goal of long-term societal...

38:47.853 --> 38:49.581
<i>Sierra 3, copy.</i>

38:52.572 --> 38:56.179
<i>Once the hit occurs, the shooter,
and the shooter only, is into the wind.</i>

38:56.279 --> 39:00.491
- <i>Off continent?</i>
- <i>Yeah, that's how Felix wants it.</i>

39:01.892 --> 39:04.596
The private sector
can no longer think only vertically,

39:04.737 --> 39:09.184
