39:40.423 --> 39:44.136
then we're destined to failure.
It's balance. It's balance.

39:51.047 --> 39:53.353
Out. Out.

40:01.185 --> 40:03.989
- You're in Spain.
- And you're in a swanky suit.

40:04.730 --> 40:06.016
Jim, why are you here?

40:09.652 --> 40:11.837
- I think you know.
- No, I don't.

40:11.937 --> 40:13.865
Believe me, I don't.
What can I do for you?

40:14.006 --> 40:16.168
Someone tried to kill me
three days ago in Congo.

40:16.642 --> 40:21.340
Oh, wow. What is that, your book title?
It's pretty good, actually.

40:21.680 --> 40:23.633
You're all writing memoirs these days.

40:24.233 --> 40:27.679
But why were you in Congo? Why?
Didn't we do them enough harm?

40:28.078 --> 40:30.589
I was drilling wells.

40:31.215 --> 40:33.904
- I was working for an NGO.
- Really?

40:34.004 --> 40:37.939
Yeah, really. Not all of us
wanna turn our sin into profit.

40:40.249 --> 40:41.526
Really?

40:42.284 --> 40:45.072
Well, let me tell you,
I don't believe a word you're saying.

40:45.571 --> 40:49.133
