55:36.512 --> 55:38.990
You cannot take her.

55:39.090 --> 55:41.901
She's mine. She's my wife.

55:42.001 --> 55:45.108
Ask her, who was there for her?

55:45.988 --> 55:48.958
Why did you come back
into our lives, Jim? Why?

55:49.058 --> 55:51.936
Get up. Move. Come on.

55:52.495 --> 55:54.997
- I can't let you take her away from me.
- Which way?

55:55.097 --> 55:57.157
- Annie?
- What's going on?

55:57.257 --> 55:59.319
- Annie!
- She's my wife. She's my wife.

56:00.811 --> 56:03.247
Get dressed. Get dressed.
